    "about_page": {
      "values": [
        {
          "title": "[DOI] Wonder",
          "emoji": "[DOI] ✨",
          "desc": "[DOI] We begin with questions, not answers. Every concept starts with a mystery, not a definition. We protect the natural curiosity every child is born with."
        },
        {
          "title": "[DOI] Equity",
          "emoji": "[DOI] ⚖️",
          "desc": "[DOI] One platform. For everyone. The child in a village in Odisha and the child in an apartment in Bengaluru should see the same beautiful concept, the same simulation, the same joy."
        },
        {
          "title": "[DOI] Respect",
          "emoji": "[DOI] 🙏",
          "desc": "[DOI] No grades, no judgment, no shame. Every learner is equal. The 6-year-old discovering colours. The 40-year-old who always wanted to understand gravity. Both are welcome here."
        },
        {
          "title": "[DOI] Patience",
          "emoji": "[DOI] 🌱",
          "desc": "[DOI] Learning takes the time it takes. No countdown timers on understanding. No pressure to move faster. The concept waits. Always."
        },
        {
          "title": "[DOI] Joy",
          "emoji": "[DOI] 🎉",
          "desc": "[DOI] If learning is not joyful, something is wrong with the design — not with the learner. Science is joyful. Mathematics is joyful. Discovery is joyful."
        },
        {
          "title": "[DOI] Identity",
          "emoji": "[DOI] 🇮🇳",
          "desc": "[DOI] Indian scientists, Indian examples, Indian languages, Indian realities. This is not a global platform translated for India. It is built for India, from India."
        }
      ],
      "difference_points": [
        {
          "emoji": "[DOI] 🔓",
          "title": "[DOI] Free by Design",
          "desc": "[DOI] There is no 'poor version' and 'rich version' of learning on Jigyasu. Everything is free. Forever. For everyone. This is not a feature. It is a principle."
        },
        {
          "emoji": "[DOI] 🌐",
          "title": "[DOI] Website First",
          "desc": "[DOI] A link shared through WhatsApp can reach a child in a village. No installation, no storage pressure, no app store barrier. Just open and learn."
        },
        {
          "emoji": "[DOI] 🗣️",
          "title": "[DOI] Mother Tongue",
          "desc": "[DOI] Thinking happens in our mother tongue. All 22 official scheduled Indian languages are fully supported, ensuring language is never a barrier to understanding."
        },
        {
          "emoji": "[DOI] 🛠️",
          "title": "[DOI] Playful Simulations",
          "desc": "[DOI] We don't just tell. We let you play. Interactive physics engines, math visualizers, and biology sandboxes turn abstract ideas into toys you can touch."
        }
      ],
